name: Reborn VR
summary: Reborn VR is a VR Social Media Platform, offering players a diverse selections of multiplayer social VR games, including PvE (Skydivers World), PvP (Gorilla Tag fan game worlds), Horror (FNAF World), and Music (Beat Saber fan game).Our SDK is now publicly available, empowering you to create and share your ideas with the global VR community. Stay tuned for upcoming updates, as we prepare to launch our Vision Pro compatible version and the highly-anticipated Sword Art Online MMO fan game.
